# Blueprint: Protagonist Character
# Este é um placeholder para o Blueprint que será criado no UE5

# Configuração do Protagonista - Dr. Marcus Chen
# Paleontologista de 35 anos, especialista em dinossauros do Cretáceo

[Character Settings]
Character Type: Protagonist
Base MetaHuman: MH_Protagonist_Base
Age: 35
Profession: Paleontologist
Specialization: Cretaceous Period Dinosaurs

[Physical Characteristics]
Height: 1.78m (Medium build)
Build: Athletic but academic (not overly muscular)
Hair: Dark brown, slightly unkempt from travel
Eyes: Hazel, intelligent and observant
Skin: Lightly tanned from outdoor work
Distinguishing Features: Small scar on left hand from excavation accident

[Starting Clothing]
Torso: Khaki field shirt, partially torn
Legs: Dark brown cargo pants with multiple pockets
Feet: Sturdy hiking boots, well-worn
Accessories: Leather satchel, broken wristwatch, field notebook

[Personality Traits]
- Curious and analytical
- Calm under pressure
- Respectful of nature
- Slightly awkward in social situations
- Passionate about paleontology

[Starting Equipment]
- Field notebook (waterlogged but readable)
- Broken compass
- Small hand trowel
- Magnifying glass
- Emergency whistle

[Character Arc]
Starts as academic observer, evolves into survivor and eventually bridge between modern knowledge and primitive world.